Changes:
 mx-updater (26.06.02mx25) mx; urgency=medium
 .
   * Fix: left-click set to MX Package Installer opened Synaptic or View and Upgrade instead.
   * Settings: "full screen" terminal size option removed from the dropdown.
   * Settings window: icon renamed from "mx-updater-settings" to "updater-mx-settings"
     to prevent Papirus icon theme from hijacking it on KDE/Plasma.
